Daniel B. Cid <daniel.cid@gmail.com>
v0.3 (2005/09/22): Added support for logcollector to read one file
                   at a time. Added automatic file ignore on syscheck.
                   Only monitor stable files. Added noalert option to
                   the rules. Hashing some of them to minimize run time
                   checking (kernel rules done). Fixed maild to wait a few
                   seconds before sending an alert. It will avoid multiple
                   alerts at the same time on different e-mails. Added
                   option for local installation. Added manage_agents to
                   deal with agents addition, etc.
                   Modified files:
                   src/headers/mq_op.h
                   src/init/init.sh
                   src/logcollector/VERSION
                   src/logcollector/config.c
                   src/logcollector/logcollector.c
